snippet.title: We Finally Know Why These Stars Got Fired From Bravo
snippet.description:
Bravo reality shows like The Real Housewives franchise and Southern Charm are famous for their drama, and it’s the main reason a lot of people tune in, but these people still managed to take it too far.

Some crossed a line, like physical violence or a serious crime, that you can’t come back from, and Bravo had to give them the boot. From the celeb of The Real Housewives of Atlanta who — oddly enough — was fired for not telling enough about her personal life to the time that even Top Chef got out of hand, here are the real reasons stars got fired from Bravo.

#Bravo #RealityTV #RealHousewives

Jeff Lewis flipped out | 0:00
Brandi Glanville had haters | 1:14
Jill Zarin’s heartbreak | 2:20
Thomas Ravenel’s controversy | 3:14
The Phaedra Parks rumor | 4:11
Jacqueline Laurita didn’t fit | 4:58
Kenya Moore didn’t peep | 5:47
Danielle Staub’s two seasons | 6:37
No more Manzos | 7:28
Tossed overboard | 8:16
A physical assault on Top Chef | 9:01
Bravo gutted its summer house | 9:48
